<section class="about-activities py-14 md:py-24 text-base-900">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 justify-center text-center mb-12">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8 md:col-start-3">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary-600">Nos Activités</h2>
        <p class="text-xl opacity-80 mb-4">
          Le Club Science Politique organise diverses activités pour enrichir l'expérience académique et professionnelle de ses membres.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-primary-600 mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
