        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-600 text-center">Publications</h3>
        <p class="text-center text-base opacity-80">Publication d'analyses et d'articles sur l'actualité politique nationale et internationale.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-primary-600 mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
